= Weather: An Autumn Leaf

<b>Version 1.0 (Jun 12, 2009)</b>

Author::    Tim Morgan (mailto:autumn@timothymorgan.info)
Copyright:: Copyright (c)2009 Tim Morgan
License::   Distributed under the same terms as Ruby.

Provides a collection of useful commands for getting weather information over
IRC.

== Usage

!weather [zip]:: Returns a textual description of the weather at a zip code.
!metar [airport]:: Displays the current weather at an airport (by ICAO code) in
                   coded METAR format.
!taf [airport]:: Displays the forecasted weather at an airport (by ICAO code) in
                 coded TAF format.
